reviewText: Bought this for my elderly in-laws and they really liked seeing the "real country" singers as they put it.  I know they have watched it several times so I guess they do like it.
If you like old country music you will love this DVD.  It is awesome to see all these old country singers on stage.

Very disappointed, the disk was only 30 min. long and the same music that was on Vol. 2 so I suggest buying 2 as the music is good and a lot longer. This was the most expensive disk we have purchased for older country music.  Definitely not worth the price.  I would have sent it back but my husband opened it before realizing what it lacked.
